title: 12/02/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 12/02/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to the voice of the SEC Paul Finebaum. He tells us why he thinks Nick Saban is worth $100 Million a year. Ross Tucker calls in to preview tonight's game between the Saints/Cowboys and tell us who he thinks should win the Heisman. And Mark Sanchez shares stories about his time at USC.
